RAWALPINDI, Jun 16 (APP):Director General Inter Services Public Relations (DG ISPR) Major General Babar Iftikhar Tuesday said Indian Army troops initiated unprovoked ceasefire violation in Bagsar Sector along the Line of Control (LOC) targeting civil population.
In a tweet, the ISPR DG said due to indiscriminate fire of Indian troops , an innocent civilian, Babar Hussain, resident of Mehtika village got injured.
